    public class BlockGUI<T extends net.minecraft.tileentity.TileEntity,C extends ContainerBase<T>>
extends BlockTE<T>
    This block registers a container to it'S tile entity and handles the gui opening when the block is right clicked. You still need to manually register the screen on the client.
